<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 02:11:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>RQ-180秘密隐形无人机似乎已紧急降落在希腊空军基地</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/secret-rq-180-stealth-drone-appears-to-have-made-an-emergency-landing-at-a-greek-air-base</link><description>&lt;p&gt;希腊的观察者特别仔细地观察到了一架似乎特别神秘的无人机。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/secret-rq-180-stealth-drone-appears-to-have-made-an-emergency-landing-at-a-greek-air-base"&gt;RQ-180 秘密隐形无人机似乎紧急降落在希腊空军&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;基地&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 23:39:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/secret-rq-180-stealth-drone-appears-to-have-made-an-emergency-landing-at-a-greek-air-base</guid></item><item><title>伊朗的能源基础设施现已列入目标清单（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/irans-energy-infrastructure-is-now-on-the-targeting-list</link><description>&lt;p&gt;南帕尔斯气田的袭击使伊朗的能源生产成为焦点，而这对伊朗政府的资金至关重要。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/irans-energy-infrastructure-is-now-on-the-targeting-list"&gt;伊朗的能源基础设施现已列入目标清单（更新）&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 22:36:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/irans-energy-infrastructure-is-now-on-the-targeting-list</guid></item><item><title>驻扎在中东的美国海军扫雷舰现已抵达新加坡</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/u-s-navy-minesweepers-stationed-in-middle-east-are-now-in-singapore</link><description>&lt;p&gt;被分配执行中东扫雷任务的三艘濒海战斗舰中的两艘又向相反的方向采取了行动。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/u-s-navy-minesweepers-stationed-in-middle-east-are-now-in-singapore"&gt;驻扎在中东的美国海军扫雷舰现已抵达新加坡后，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 19:45:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/u-s-navy-minesweepers-stationed-in-middle-east-are-now-in-singapore</guid></item><item><title>美国使用新型 5000 磅地堡破坏者袭击伊朗反舰导弹基地：报告</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/u-s-used-its-new-5000-pound-bunker-busters-to-hit-iranian-anti-ship-missile-sites-reports</link><description>&lt;p&gt;GBU-72/B 位于常见的 2,000 磅掩体破坏者和更强大的 30,000 磅 GBU-57/B 大型穿甲弹之间。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/u-s-used-its-new-5000-pound-bunker-busters-to-hit-iranian-anti-ship-missile-sites-reports"&gt;美国使用新型 5,000 磅地堡破坏者袭击伊朗反舰导弹基地：报道&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 15:49:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/u-s-used-its-new-5000-pound-bunker-busters-to-hit-iranian-anti-ship-missile-sites-reports</guid></item><item><title>海军努力维持航母的生存计划（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-juggles-its-aircraft-carrier-plans-to-stay-afloat</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一艘航母在起火前就已经疲惫不堪，另一艘航母的使用寿命第二次延长，而第三艘航母的交付则被推迟。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-juggles-its-aircraft-carrier-plans-to-stay-afloat"&gt;海军努力维持其航空母舰的生存计划（已更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 23:50:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-juggles-its-aircraft-carrier-plans-to-stay-afloat</guid></item><item><title>特朗普不再希望盟友派遣军舰打开霍尔木兹海峡（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-no-longer-wants-allies-to-send-warships-to-open-the-strait-of-hormuz</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在盟友拒绝他向该海峡派遣军舰的要求一天后，特朗普宣布“我们不需要任何人的帮助！”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-no-longer-wants-allies-to-send-warships-to-open-the-strait-of-hormuz"&gt;特朗普不再希望盟友派遣军舰打开霍尔木兹海峡（更新）的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 23:17:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-no-longer-wants-allies-to-send-warships-to-open-the-strait-of-hormuz</guid></item><item><title>海军 E-2D 鹰眼战斗机似乎正赶往中东</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/navy-e-2d-hawkeye-radar-planes-appear-to-be-rushing-to-the-middle-east</link><description>&lt;p&gt;E-2D 是美国最有能力发现正在对海湾阿拉伯国家造成严重破坏的无人机和其他低空飞行的伊朗威胁的平台。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/navy-e-2d-hawkeye-radar-planes-appear-to-be-rushing-to-the-middle-east"&gt;海军 E-2D 鹰眼战机似乎正赶往中东&lt;/a&gt;首次出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;中。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 22:50:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/navy-e-2d-hawkeye-radar-planes-appear-to-be-rushing-to-the-middle-east</guid></item><item><title>日本 EC-2 电子战喷气机，可以说是世界上最丑的飞机，刚刚首次飞行</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/the-worlds-ugliest-airplane-just-flew-for-the-first-time</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在军用飞机设计日益同质化的世界中，鸭嘴兽般的川崎 EC-2 是一个彻底的异类。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/the-worlds-ugliest-airplane-just-flew-for-the-first-time"&gt;日本的 EC-2 电子战喷气式飞机，可以说是世界上最丑的飞机，刚刚首次飞行，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 19:08:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/the-worlds-ugliest-airplane-just-flew-for-the-first-time</guid></item><item><title>盟友拒绝特朗普向霍尔木兹海峡派遣军舰的要求（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/allies-push-back-on-trumps-demand-they-send-warships-to-strait-of-hormuz</link><description>&lt;p&gt;德国周一断然拒绝了特朗普关于北约盟国派遣海军舰艇帮助保护这条战略水道航运的要求。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/allies-push-back-on-trumps-demand-they-send-warships-to-strait-of-hormuz"&gt;盟友拒绝特朗普向霍尔木兹海峡派遣军舰的要求（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 23:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/allies-push-back-on-trumps-demand-they-send-warships-to-strait-of-hormuz</guid></item><item><title>携带新旧干扰吊舱混合负载的 EA-18G 咆哮者正在执行伊朗任务</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/ea-18g-growler-with-split-load-of-new-and-old-jamming-pods-seen-supporting-iran-strikes</link><description>&lt;p&gt;五角大楼的一份报告称，尽管新吊舱正在被用于活跃的冲突中，但它们仍然存在严重的初期问题。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/ea-18g-growler-with-split-load-of-new-and-old-jamming-pods-seen-supporting-iran-strikes"&gt;携带新旧干扰吊舱混合负载的 EA-18G 咆哮者飞机正在执行伊朗任务，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 21:53:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/ea-18g-growler-with-split-load-of-new-and-old-jamming-pods-seen-supporting-iran-strikes</guid></item></channel></rss>